# Phase 10 — Sales Premium & Yield Predictor Engine

## What Was Built

Phase 10 adds a deterministic engine that quantifies the financial return of upgrading fitout quality in UAE real estate projects. It answers the core investor question: *"If I spend +X AED/sqm on better finishes, how much does my yield increase and sale price improve?"*

