## Engine Design

### [computeValueAddBridge(inputs)](file:///Users/amrosaleh/Maiyar/miyar-v2/server/engines/value-add-engine.ts#90-220) → [ValueAddResult](file:///Users/amrosaleh/Maiyar/miyar-v2/shared/miyar-types.ts#246-257)
- **Yield Delta**: Percentage point increase in gross rental yield from upgrading fitout
- **Sale Premium**: % and AED uplift vs area median based on fitout ratio bands
- **Payback Period**: Months to recover incremental fitout cost from rental premium
- **Confidence**: Derived from DLD transaction count (high ≥15, medium 8-14, low 3-7, insufficient <3)
- **Risk Flags**: `UNDER_SPEC`, `DIMINISHING_RETURNS` (over-spec at >28% fitout ratio)

### [computeBrandEquityForecast(inputs)](file:///Users/amrosaleh/Maiyar/miyar-v2/server/engines/value-add-engine.ts#223-293) → [BrandEquityResult](file:///Users/amrosaleh/Maiyar/miyar-v2/shared/miyar-types.ts#265-271)
- **Halo Effect**: Trophy/Ultra-luxury branded projects at >10% outperformance generate 3-8% portfolio uplift
- **Formula**: [(salePerformancePct - 10) × 0.35](file:///Users/amrosaleh/Maiyar/miyar-v2/server/_core/llm.ts#35-43), clamped at 8%, + 15% brand bonus for branded
- **Portfolio Impact**: AED estimates at small/medium/large next-project scenarios

