## Frontend

**Section F: Sales Premium & Yield Predictor** added to Investor Summary page:

- Two interactive range sliders (current vs proposed fitout AED/sqm)
- 300ms debounced live queries to `salesPremium.getValueAddBridge`
- 4 KPI cards: Yield Uplift, Sale Premium, Payback Period, Incremental Cost
- Confidence badge with tooltip explanation
- Risk flag warnings (amber alert panel)
- Brand Equity Halo panel (only shows for Trophy/Ultra-luxury branded projects)
- Auto-initializes sliders from project's computed costPerSqm

---

## Architecture Compliance

| Principle | ✅ Compliance |
|-----------|--------------|
| Pure functions only | Engine has zero DB imports |
| Three scenarios | Conservative/mid/aggressive everywhere |
| AED everywhere | All monetary outputs in AED |
| No LLM in calculations | Fully deterministic math |
| Confidence levels | Derived from DLD transaction count |
